SAFETY NOTICE: This project controls a machine with large rotating blades that
can cause serious injury or death. It is provided for educational and research
purposes. Anyone building or operating it is solely responsible for safe
construction, testing, supervision, and compliance with local law. Keep the
blades disconnected until every failsafe is proven. See docs/BUILD.md §0.

